summary: This is an email from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York regarding the location of an FBI 302 interview report from August 2007. The email indicates the 302 was found, saved to a shared drive, and attached to the email.

persons.name: Assistant United States Attorney
persons.context: Sender of the email who conducted a search for and located an FBI 302 interview report from August 2007, saving it to a shared drive.

events.title: August 2007 Interview
events.description: An interview was conducted, documented in an FBI 302 report. The specific subject of the interview is not named in this email.

locations: United States Attorney's Office Southern District of New York
keyFacts: An FBI 302 report documenting an interview from August 7, 2007, was the subject of a search.
The 302 report was located and saved to a shared drive in a 'witness folder' and a 'witness 3500 folder'.
The email correspondence about this document occurred on July 29, 2021.
The communication originated from an Assistant United States Attorney in the SDNY.
